### API test pakai REST Client VS Code Extension
### Harus sudah jalan server di localhost:8080
### Klik "Send Request" di atas setiap request

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

#categories

### GET All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories

### GET Category by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1

### POST Create Category
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Elektronik",
    "description": "Kategori untuk barang elektronik"
}

### PUT Update Category
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Makanan Updated",
    "description": "Kategori makanan yang sudah diupdate"
}

### DELETE Category
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/4

#products

### GET All Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/produk

### GET Product by ID (dengan category_name dari JOIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/produk/1

### POST Create Product (dengan category_id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/produk
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Ayam Panggang",
    "price": 30000,
    "stock": 50,
    "category_id": 1
}

### PUT Update Product
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/produk/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Nasi Goreng Spesial",
    "price": 18000,
    "stock": 45,
    "category_id": 1
}

### DELETE Product
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/produk/5
